&lt;p&gt;What&apos;s happening there is the slave is connecting to the backup but is not being allowed to register as a slave because the backup is not yet a master. The logging should reflect what&apos;s actually happening.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also, after the backup is promoted and the slave properly registers, there&apos;s nothing in the slaves logs.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
